tn.misc

Class LinkPropertyFunction<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tn.misc.LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>
      • tn.misc.LinkPropertyFunction<T>

  • public class LinkPropertyFunction<T>
extends LinkReadOnlyProperty<T>
    Description:

    This class creates a wrapper for a function to be applied to a certain link property. It enables accessing the function, and making a copy of it.
